getSum

public static float getSum(String[] values,
                           int startIndex,
                           int endIndex)
Parses the String array as float and calculates the sum of all elements. The calculation will sum up all elements between startIndex until endIndex-1, so endIndex is excluded.

Parameters:
startIndex - start index
endIndex - end index
Returns:
the biggest value within the range
